# %% [Code Cell 10] — DYNAMIC WAVE FORCING GENERATOR (MULTI-TPAR FOR SWAN)
# ==============================================================================================
# PATCH v3.1: Auto Directional Spreading & Multi-Format Exporter (.TPAR / .BCW)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# APA ITU DIRECTIONAL SPREADING?
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Format TPAR SWAN: "YYYYMMDD.HHMMSS  Hs  Tp  Dir  Spread"
# Format BCW SWAN:  Satu berkas gabungan terstruktur dengan waktu relatif (menit)
#
# "Spread" = standar deviasi (σθ) distribusi arah energi gelombang (dalam derajat).
# Bukan arah gelombang itu sendiri, tapi seberapa TERSEBAR energinya di sekitar Dir.
#
#   σθ kecil (~10°)  → swell murni: energi terfokus sempit (gelombang perjalanan jauh)
#   σθ besar (~30°)  → sea angin lokal: energi tersebar lebar ke segala arah
#
# SUMBER DATA SPREADING (urutan prioritas otomatis):
#   1. ERA5 'dwi'  (directional width of wind wave spectrum) → radian → konversi ×(180/π)
#   2. ERA5 'dspr' (directional spread, beberapa dataset ERA5-Ocean)  → degrees langsung
#   3. ERA5 'dwww' (directional width of wind waves)                  → radian
#   4. Physics fallback: ε = Hs/L₀, L₀ = g·Tp²/(2π) → spread = clip(10+333ε, 10°, 30°)
#   5. Manual override (widget)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CHANGELOG v3.1:
#   + Dropdown format ekspor: "TPAR (Multiple Files)" atau "BCW (Single Combined File)"
#   + Generator BCW fisis: konversi waktu absolut ke menit relatif dari index-0
#   + Header BCW multi-titik otomatis: WaveHeight, WavePeriod, WaveDirection, WaveSpreading
#   + Susunan baris data terkelompok berdasarkan variabel (bukan berdasarkan titik)
#   + Panduan integrasi dinamis D-Waves (.mdw) di panel log akhir
# ==============================================================================================

